title: Gunspell v.1.0.19
description:
Great Free-to-Play RPG-Adventure game where guns and magic act together! You will be caught in a series of unbelievable events. 

Vampires and demons, heroes and monsters await you in realms of Gunspell.
- Match3 battles with a lot of features
- Many different strange worlds to explore
- Hordes of enemies to fight
- Tons of different weapons, items and spells!
- Perfect Graphics!

What's new in version 1.0.19:
- Fixed some critical bugs

What's new in version 1.0.18:
- Now you can see spells stats during the pause
- GUI was reworked and made faster
- Fixed enemies' weapons localization

System requirements:
- 1 Ghz CPU and better (ARMv7)
- 512 MB RAM

Released by developer. Timely updates are coming.
